text: Hi, for anyone new to this (such as myself), i was just viewing a channel on Youtube - Horsetrader, he only has circa 10 videos, but you may find them useful. Ive just watched his video on login and session management and although Ive been through these steps over the last few days, it would have been easier to have watched that first. All his videos are based on python, so worth a mention.
